  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To evaluate effect on comorbid disease and weight loss five years after Roux-en-Y gastric
      bypass (RYGB) surgery for morbid obesity.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Morbid obese patient frequently have comorbid diseases, e.g. diabetes, hypertension,
      hyperlipidemia, and sleep apnea. We will study the remission rate and weight loss five years
      after Roux-en-Y gastric bypass (RYGB) surgery in a nationwide large group of patients.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
